OL,6,FIt added there are "serious concerns
OL,7,Fabout the urgency of the work and need
OL,8,Ffor a sustainable long-term financing
OL,9,Fplan" and emphasised that housing
OL,10,Fprojects can not go ahead until the
OL,11,Fsewage system is looked at.
OL,13,FWhile the new Sewage Treatment Works
OL,14,Fat Bellozanne can deal with waste for
OL,15,Fup to 140,000 people, the pipes
OL,16,Fstretching out across the island need
OL,17,Fimproving.
