OL,3,CSewage system needs #52 million
OL,4,Cupgrade for new homes to be built
OL,6,FOver #15 million has already been set
OL,7,Faside for improvements, with Jersey's
OL,8,FInfrastructure Minster Andy Jehan
OL,9,Fpromising to work with colleagues to
OL,10,Fringfence extra money.
OL,12,FHe added: "We've got this funding for
OL,13,Fthis year and the next year, but we
OL,14,Fneed more funding so we can get the
OL,15,Fsewage coming here directly rather
OL,16,Fthan coming in tankers."
