OL,3,CSewage system needs #52 million
OL,4,Cupgrade for new homes to be built
OL,6,FDeputy Steve Luce, Chair of the Panel,
OL,7,Fsays: "Our mains drain network is now
OL,8,Fhaving to service a population almost
OL,9,Ftwice the size of that which it was
OL,10,Fdesigned to cope with."
OL,12,F"For our drainage network to continue
OL,13,Fto operate as it should we need to
OL,14,Fincrease this capacity and do it
OL,15,Fquickly."
OL,17,FPart of the current funding will go
OL,18,Ftowards building new storage tanks,
OL,19,Fsimilar to the cavern in Snow Hill.
