OL,3,CSewage system needs #52 million
OL,4,Cupgrade for new homes to be built
OL,6,FJersey's Assistant Infrastructure
OL,7,FMinister, Deputy Steve Ahier, agrees
OL,8,Fmajor improvements to the island's
OL,9,Fsewage system are needed.
OL,11,FHe explained: "I'd like to reassure
OL,12,Fislanders that this is a priority.
OL,14,F"A lot of the existing network was
OL,15,Fbuilt back in the 1950s, or even
OL,16,Fearlier, and is already at its limits
OL,17,F... that's why additional funding of
OL,18,F#15.6m was allocated in the recently-
OL,19,Fagreed Government Plan. We can now
OL,20,Fstep up this work, but future funding
OL,21,Fis required after 2025."
